variable.name: x-amtrak-trace-id
variable.description: Per-request trace/session identifier used in request headers; stored in sessionStorage as ibsession.sessionid and should be resolved dynamically at runtime.

explanation: The value maps to the sessionStorage entry ibsession.sessionid and is used as the x-amtrak-trace-id header in the identified request. It is session-scoped and must be resolved dynamically during a live session.
